Class Animal

  • java.lang.Object
    • Animal
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bird, Lion, Snake, Zebra
    public class Animal
extends java.lang.Object
    Animal class, creates general information about an animal in a zoo. Serves as a superclass for all specific animal types.
